{"tid":2172421,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK Jennie新畫報公開！無法忍受她「露肉」的粉絲們...各種P圖都出現了 XD","createTime":"2020-08-24T14:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T04:01:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"098491bd0da40a0652498d854a319fe419b6152a","tid":2172421,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_499526a1c8789dc8ac43a116b64bca9e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-24/129506-868329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_499526a1c8789dc8ac43a116b64bca9e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-24%2F129506-868329.jpg&h=e344aa7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK成員Jennie近日為《ELLE KOREA》拍攝了一組美妝畫報。<br />\n<br />\n以柔和、幹練的風格為妝容（使用HERA產品）概念造型進行了拍攝，畫報中搭配的色彩也都是由Jennie親自挑選。不管什麼樣的妝容，Jennie也用自己的風格完美消化，吸引了大家的視線。<br />\n<br />\n當中Jennie有照片露了胸、腿，結果粉絲們馬上P圖用弄了毯子幫她蓋住，讓不少網友也表示：「好可愛ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ」、「毯子被利用了，抱走才是目的」、「粉絲怎麼這麼有趣」、「粉絲們都很厲害呢，各個是鬼才」、「連圖都畫得好可愛」等等。<br />\n<br />\n而BLACKPINK在今年6月發行《How You Like That》寫下各種紀錄，她們將在28日發行新曲《Ice Cream》，並由Selena Gomez參與Feat.，近日陸續公開了預告片、成員預告照，這次的新曲又會引發什麼熱潮？也備受關注。"},{"pid":"2f30df30387d035d844d4d7ae7ccdc37bc01bd62","tid":2172421,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":32,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_af1d1d8397445fffd12bf05fc5e48c06/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-24/129506-868318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_af1d1d8397445fffd12bf05fc5e48c06%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-24%2F129506-868318.jpg&h=a729938b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1f1e55315be3a6866025c39a98b5c639/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-24/129506-868319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1f1e55315be3a6866025c39a98b5c639%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-24